      "rationale": "Validation performed on production-representative non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw hardware under ASTM F1717 compression-bending, which is the exact test modality referenced in the COU. Two-laboratory design strengthens generalizability. Validation activities are directly applicable to the regulatory credibility claim."
